msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Public application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. "
"Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page."
msgstr ""
"Formulaire de candidature public pour les artistes souhaitant rejoindre le "
"réseau Agnosis. Soumet au point de terminaison REST d’admission. Placez ceci "
"sur votre page /join/."

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "join"
msgstr "rejoindre"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "apply"
msgstr "postuler"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "application"
msgstr "candidature"

#: blocks/join/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "admission"
msgstr "admission"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Newsletter Popover"
msgstr "Menu contextuel de la newsletter"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Bouton icône qui ouvre un menu contextuel en plein écran contenant le "
"formulaire d’inscription à la newsletter. Autonome — placez-le directement "
"dans un modèle d’en-tête ou de pied de page ; n’affiche rien lorsque la "
"newsletter publique est désactivée (Réglages → Newsletter)."

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "newsletter"
msgstr "newsletter"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "subscribe"
msgstr "s’abonner"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "popover"
msgstr "menu contextuel"

#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "footer"
msgstr "pied de page"

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Newsletter Signup"
msgstr "Inscription à la newsletter"

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Email signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the "
"newsletter subscribe REST endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Formulaire d’inscription par e-mail pour la newsletter publique (double "
"confirmation). Envoie les données vers le point de terminaison REST "
"d’abonnement à la newsletter."

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "email"
msgstr "e-mail"

#: blocks/newsletter-signup/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "signup"
msgstr "inscription"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "My Submissions"
msgstr "Mes envois"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Affiche les brouillons de soumissions d’œuvres de l’artiste connecté en "
"attente de relecture et d’approbation. Placez-le sur votre page /my-"
"submissions/ ou dans un modèle de l’Éditeur de site."

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "submissions"
msgstr "soumissions"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block keyword"
msgid "review"
msgstr "relecture"

